					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11237741#post-4222839</guid>
				<title>Intruders Are Not Welcome</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11237741/scp-4522#post-4222839</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2019 15:13:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Woedenaz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404096</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hello, friends!</p> <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3QEouFGNtY">Official Track for this SCP</a>, as Chosen by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> <p>This is an SCP born from the SCPD Draft Swap and based off <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>'s draft :D</p> <p>Many thanks to the following for Crit:<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> (of course)<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555601656" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" >Tufto</a></span></p> <p>Here are the most important Image Sources:</p> <p><a href="https://wellcomecollection.org/works/jq926hwk#licenseInformation">The Monkey Image is from here.</a> — Creative Commons Attribution (CC BY 4.0)<br /> <a href="https://pixnio.com/flora-plants/fruits/peaches-pictures/peach-food-healthy-fruit-sweet-diet-vitamin-delicious">The Peach Image is from here.</a> — Creative Commons Attribution (CC0)</p> <p>Hope you all enjoy! &lt;3</p> <p><span style="font-size:75%;">I'll probably edit this later and add some author commentary. But I just wanted to get this up for now. :D</span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
